# What is Bombay?

A minimal set of non-OO libraries for punk programmers uisng PHP 5.3+.


`/index.php`:

``` php
<?php

	require '/path/to/bombay.php';

	// include only the libs you need
	requires ('helpers', 'template', 'form');

	// do your thang...

?>
```


Now go build [web applications][1].



